kpi_info.title: period_duration
kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.

kpi_info.title: NSCURRENT
kpi_info.use: Number of normal subscribers for each locationarea at the reporting time. The maximum number of location areas in a report is 40.

kpi_info.title: NSAVERAGE
kpi_info.use: Average number of normal subscribers foreach location area during the reporting period. For the calculation of the average, the number of subscribers in the location area is interrogated at five-minute intervals. The maximum number of location areas in a report is 40.

kpi_info.title: SIM_CURRENT_REG
kpi_info.use:
Number of subscribers at the end of the Result Accumulation Period in the given Location Area with triplet authentication vector in VLR fetched from HLR/AUC. Old counter (M80B2C3 - CURRENT) is not available with this counter.
Measured object: VLR

kpi_info.title: SIM_AVG_REG
kpi_info.use:
Average number of subscribers during the Result Accumulation Period in the given Location Area who have triplet authentication vectors in VLR. For the calculation of the average, the number of SIM subscribers is interrogated at five-minute intervals. Old counter (M80B2C4 - AVERAGE) is not available with this counter.
Measured object: VLR
